3. **CI/CD** (Recommended)
   - Connect GitHub repository
   - Enable auto-deploy on push to main
   - Configure preview deployments for PRs

4. **Security**
   - Rotate JWT_SECRET regularly
   - Enable Railway private networking
   - Review access controls

